description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of drugs for Malawi) is a component of Malawi Health Sector Support Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £10,349,324. This component benefits Malawi, and works in the following sector(s): Basic health care. , with the following implementing partners: AECOM, Charles Kendall Group. The start date is 03-03-2013 and the end date is 30-12-2016.
